abstract: Financially strapped United Football League cancels final two weeks of its season and goes straight to championship game, in which Virginia Destoyers defeat Las Vegas Locomotives, 17-3.
snippet: The United Football League canceled the final two weeks of its season and went straight to Friday night’s championship game.
lead_paragraph: The United Football League canceled the final two weeks of its season and went straight to Friday night’s championship game.

headline.main: A Struggling Football League Skips a Beat and Crowns a Champion
headline.print_headline: A League in Dire Need of Some Wins Crowns a Champion
headline.seo: A Struggling Football League Skips a Beat and Crowns a Champion
